{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_04_03",
  "title": "神崎莉央",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――写真撮影当日",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "映画の雰囲気に一番合いそうな衣装を\n選んでみたんだけど、どうかしら？",
      "startTime": 5.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "よく似合ってますよ\nこれならケイティにも負けていません",
      "startTime": 10.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "彼女はこんなものじゃないわ！\nケイティをバカにしないで！",
      "startTime": 14.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "褒めたのに怒られた……",
      "startTime": 17.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……\n貴方はケイティへのリスペクトが足りないのよ",
      "startTime": 21.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、今日のために仕上げてきた\n私の体はどうかしら？",
      "startTime": 27.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "どう、この力こぶ。貴方よりあるんじゃないかしら\n腹筋もカチカチよ。触ってみる？",
      "startTime": 34.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、さすがに触るのはやめておきます……",
      "startTime": 37.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……。とはいえ、ここまで体を作り込むのは\nちょっと女の子らしくなかったかもしれないわね",
      "startTime": 46.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺は莉央さんらしくていいと思いますよ\n撮影のために頑張った証ですから",
      "startTime": 52.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう\nそろそろ撮影が始まるわね",
      "startTime": 57.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "見ていてね。ケイティそっくりとはいかないけど\n私らしいクールな写真にしてみせるわ",
      "startTime": 64,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影が終わって、数日後",
      "startTime": 67.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 69.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "この間撮影した写真の画像が送られてきたので\n一緒に確認してもらっていいですか？",
      "startTime": 73.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "もう写真が出来上がったの？\nどんな仕上がりになったのか楽しみだわ",
      "startTime": 78.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……いいじゃない、これ",
      "startTime": 83.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "まるで映画のワンシーンみたいね\n今にも作品が始まりそうだわ",
      "startTime": 89.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "衣装もばっちりハマっていて\n頑張って体を鍛えた甲斐がありましたね",
      "startTime": 95.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "そっくりとはいかなかったけど\n体を絞って、殺陣を勉強して、ポーズを研究して……",
      "startTime": 100.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "最高の一枚を撮るためにやれることは全部やったわ",
      "startTime": 106.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "この撮影のために私が陰で努力をしていたなんて\n見ている人は気付かないでしょうね……",
      "startTime": 114.5333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "……私はケイティのように\nヒロインの魅力をちゃんと表現出来たかしら？",
      "startTime": 119.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "クールで格好いいヒロインの魅力が伝わってくる\n莉央さんらしい、いい写真ですよ",
      "startTime": 126.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "仕事で好きな映画に携われるなんて\nこんなことが出来るのもアイドルならではね",
      "startTime": 132.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "私はこの写真に映画への想いを込めた……\n写真を見た人に、私の想いは伝わるかしら……",
      "startTime": 140.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "想いはきっと伝わりますよ\nその証拠に、これを見て下さい",
      "startTime": 147.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "これは……映画の宣伝部から私宛てにメール？\nええと、「急なご連絡で失礼します」",
      "startTime": 156.7333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "「現在、映画のプロモーションのために\nケイティが来日しているのですが」",
      "startTime": 164.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "「ケイティに今回の写真を見せたところ、大絶賛で\nぜひ神崎さんに会ってみたいと言って……」ええっ！？",
      "startTime": 172.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "どうやら、来日中のケイティが\n莉央さんに会いたがっているみたいですね",
      "startTime": 179.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、彼女は過密スケジュールで、今すぐホテルに\n行かないと会えないみたいですが……どうしますか？",
      "startTime": 186.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "え……今からケイティに会う？　……待って。無理",
      "startTime": 190.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "無理ですか。急な話だし仕方ないですね\n分かりました。俺から断りの連絡を入れておきます",
      "startTime": 200.2333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待って。何勝手に断ろうとしてるのよ",
      "startTime": 204.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも今無理って……",
      "startTime": 207.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの「無理」はそういう意味じゃないわ！\n会いに行くに決まってるでしょ！",
      "startTime": 213.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "憧れのハリウッドスターに会えるチャンスなんて\n二度とないかもしれないんだから……",
      "startTime": 218.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "チャンスは決して逃がさない！\nそれがLizNoirの神崎莉央よ！",
      "startTime": 223.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんらしいですね\n分かりました。じゃあ、早速出発しましょう",
      "startTime": 228.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio026.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、そうね\n今からケイティに会う……今からケイティに……",
      "startTime": 234.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio027.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……やっぱり緊張するわね",
      "startTime": 238.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio028.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、{user}さん！\n絶対に部屋までついて来るのよ！",
      "startTime": 244.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio029.m4a",
      "text": "私を独りにして外で待ってるとか言い出したら\n許さないんだから！",
      "startTime": 250.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "……クールで格好いい莉央さんにも\n可愛いところがあるんですね",
      "startTime": 254.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
